const JobData=[
    {
        "id": 1,
        "area": "Burnaby, BC",
        "position": "Marketing Coordinator",
        "initialRegistration":"December 5 2019",
        "brief": "This is a full-time position.",
        "expedited": false
    },
    {
        "id": 2,
        "area": "Burnaby, BC",
        "position": "Mobile Developer",
        "initialRegistration":"December 19 2019",
        "brief": "The Mobile Developer will design & develop software applications (apps) for mobile phones, Smartphones, Tablets, and other mobile devices. You may develop on one or more mobile platforms, including Apple iOS and Google Android. This is a permanent full-time position.",
        "expedited": false
    },
    {
        "id": 3,
        "area": "Burnaby, BC",
        "position": "Back-End Developer",
        "initialRegistration":"December 19 2019",
        "brief": "Back-End Developer(Mid-level to Senior Level) will be instrumental in the architecture and implementation of a robust, scalable backend system. The roles will design RESTful APIs, architect event-driven backend systems. This is a permanent full-time position.",
        "expedited": false
    },
    {
        "id": 4,
        "area": "Burnaby, BC",
        "position": "Web Developer",
        "initialRegistration":"December 19 2019",
        "brief": "Web developer will work closely with other teams to develop a variety of web-based products, enhancements, and new features across the various brands of our company including websites, in-app webpages, event or ad pages and so on. This is a permanent full-time position.",
        "expedited": false
    },
  ]
  
  export default JobData;
